description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=0/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Test your reflexes in this fast-paced, one-button classic. Race through procedurally generated levels, dodging obstacles in your path. Can you complete the twisted loop that is Mobius?
